# n8n Workflow: Mostaql Projects Scraper + Telegram Alerts

## Overview
This workflow scrapes new freelance projects from **Mostaql.com** every hour, filters them by keywords, and sends nicely formatted notifications to Telegram.

---

## Workflow Structure

```
1. Cron Trigger (Every Hour)
        ↓
2. HTTP Request → Fetch https://mostaql.com/projects
        ↓
3. HTML Extract / Edit Fields → Extract Job Data
        ↓
4. Code Node (Filter by Keywords) → Optional
        ↓
5. Code Node (Format Messages) → Combine + Split long messages
        ↓
6. Telegram Node → Send Message(s)
```

---

## 1. Cron Trigger
- **Node**: Schedule / Cron
- **Cron Expression**: `0 * * * *` (every hour)
- Or use "Every Hour" in the friendly interface.

---

## 2. HTTP Request Node
- **Method**: GET
- **URL**: `https://mostaql.com/projects`
- **Headers** (recommended):
  - `User-Agent`: `Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36`
  - `Accept-Language`: `ar,en-US;q=0.9,en;q=0.8`

---

## 3. HTML Extract / Edit Fields Node

```json
{
  "startUrl": "https://mostaql.com/projects",
  "fields": [
    {
      "name": "JobTitle",
      "selector": "div.card--title > h2 > a",
      "value": "text"
    },
    {
      "name": "PostTime",
      "selector": "div.card--title > ul.project__meta.list-meta-items > li.text-muted > time",
      "value": "text"
    },
    {
      "name": "Link",
      "selector": "div.card--title > h2 > a",
      "value": "attribute",
      "attribute": "href"
    }
  ]
}
```

---

## 4. Filter Code Node (Optional)

```javascript
const keywords = ["python", "فلاتر", "react", "django", "AI", "ذكاء اصطناعي", "flutter"];

const filtered = items.filter(item => {
    const title = (item.json.JobTitle || "").toLowerCase();
    const time = (item.json.PostTime || "").toLowerCase();

    return keywords.some(k => 
        title.includes(k.toLowerCase()) || time.includes(k.toLowerCase())
    );
});

return filtered;
```

---

## 5. Format Message Code Node (Final Version)

```javascript
const MAX_LENGTH = 4000;
let messages = [];
let currentMessage = `🔔 <b>مشاريع جديدة على مستقل (${items.length})</b>\n\n`;

items.forEach((item, index) => {
    const job = item.json;

    let jobText = `<b>${index + 1}. ${job.JobTitle || 'بدون عنوان'}</b>\n`;

    if (job.PostTime) jobText += `🕒 ${job.PostTime}\n`;

    if (job.Link) {
        jobText += `🔗 <a href="https://mostaql.com${job.Link}">افتح المشروع</a>\n`;
    }

    jobText += `────────────────────\n\n`;

    if ((currentMessage.length + jobText.length) > MAX_LENGTH && currentMessage.length > 100) {
        messages.push(currentMessage);
        currentMessage = `🔔 <b>مشاريع جديدة على مستقل (تابع)</b>\n\n`;
    }

    currentMessage += jobText;
});

if (currentMessage.length > 100) {
    messages.push(currentMessage);
}

return messages.map(msg => ({ json: { message: msg } }));
```

---

## 6. Telegram Node
- **Operation**: Send Message
- **Parse Mode**: **HTML** (Very Important!)
- **Message**: `{{ $json.message }}`
- **Credential**: Your Telegram Bot

---

## Tips & Improvements

- Add more fields later (Budget, Category, Description)
- Add keyword filtering
- Add error handling with "Error Trigger" or "IF" node
- Use "Wait" node if you want delays between messages
- Consider adding proxy or rotating User-Agent for heavy usage

---

**Created on:** June 11, 2026  
**For:** Mostaql.com Scraper Workflow

---
